{"TopicId":104259,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Poster Making Challenge (Recruitment Posters)","CreatedByName":"mangekyou-sama","CreatedById":83517,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-16T15:05:15Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"mangekyou-sama","CreatedById":83517,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-16T15:05:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAre you good in image-editing/compositing? If you have the skills in Photoshop or GIMP or any image-editing program, this might just be the challenge to show your PR/marketing skills!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe challenge is quite simple. People here have their respective \u0022companies\u0022. \u003Cstrong\u003EYou just have to design a poster for recruiting \u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:line-through;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eunsuspecting\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E kerbals to join your \u0022company\u0022\u003C/strong\u003E. Something like \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#B22222;\u0022\u003E\u0022Sign up now for our very first trip to Eve! [return not guaranteed]\u0022\u003C/span\u003E, or maybe something like \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#B22222;\u0022\u003E\u0022Uncle Gene wants you!\u0022\u003C/span\u003E, or maybe \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#B22222;\u0022\u003E\u0022Join the \u0026lt;x company\u0026gt; engineering team today and get a free snack!\u0022\u003C/span\u003E.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003EMECHANICS:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000080;\u0022\u003EThere are no specific dimensions for the poster itself but portrait orientation is preferred.\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000080;\u0022\u003EMake it as compelling as possible! Choice of words might just be the key to a more \u0022believable\u0022 poster.\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#000080;\u0022\u003EQuality is top priority. Don\u0027t just whip something up in paint... please \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGET DESIGNING AND POST! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Columbia","CreatedById":135031,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-16T16:12:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGood challenge! I\u0027ll put an entry soon.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Slam_Jones","CreatedById":125101,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-16T18:02:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027m no artist, but I love this challenge! Can\u0027t wait to see what folks come up with \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u0022Keep Calm and Strut On\u0022 \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-16T18:05:00Z\u0022 title=\u002204/16/2015 06:05  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 16, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Slam_Jones\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lhathron the Elf","CreatedById":118706,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-16T18:23:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u00C3\u00A8\u00C2\u00B0\u00CB\u2020\u00C3\u00A8\u00C2\u00AF\u00C2issounds\u00C3\u00A6\u00C2\u00C2\u00B6\u00C3\u00A6\u00E2\u201A\u00AC\u00C2\u00A7\u00C3\u00A6\u00C2\u00AC\u00C2\u00A1\u00C3\u00A5\u00C2\u00C2\u00AC \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: whoops, had the Chinese language bar switched on....\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis sounds exiting. I have a feeling people will have fun with this. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-16T18:23:42Z\u0022 title=\u002204/16/2015 06:23  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 16, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Lhathron the Elf\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Ethose chinese....\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sovnheim","CreatedById":104593,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-17T02:11:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI love the idea.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll try to come up with something, I\u0027ll let you know \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: I found a picture of Jeb online but it made me laugh so I just added a caption. The link with the topic is limited, however.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://img11.hostingpics.net/pics/974030kerbalspacemunlandingbyequestrianponyd5v3ptg.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022974030kerbalspacemunlandingbyequestrianponyd5v3ptg.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-17T02:45:15Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2015 02:45  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Sovnheim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-17T02:18:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E*Evil cackling*\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003EI shall see you soon, challenge...\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ghostbuzzer7","CreatedById":138096,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-17T02:20:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI seek great interest now because the member above me. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/WA9TwtG.png\u0022 alt=\u0022WA9TwtG.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tg626","CreatedById":112361,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-17T06:34:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0022You but them...\u0022?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wossname","CreatedById":118005,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-17T17:39:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI am going for the not entirely subtle 1941 Koviet style.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/vbaZy1h.png\u0022 alt=\u0022vbaZy1h.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EStarted out with a photo-shoot on the launchpad, then pasted in the lettering and the KSP \u0022retro\u0022 logo. Posterize filter on the main image, then added some blur, then some HSV noise and finally desaturated a bit to make it look old and somewhat faded. Took about 45 minutes in GIMP. Had fun with this one.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-17T17:49:52Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2015 05:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by wossname\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Slam_Jones","CreatedById":125101,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-17T17:51:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EInspiration taken from WWII posters\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/JZL0JFq.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022JZL0JFq.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso, an after-school special:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/QNM7l8e.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022QNM7l8e.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-17T17:54:07Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2015 05:54  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Slam_Jones\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ghostbuzzer7","CreatedById":138096,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-17T23:48:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt is being made currently at 3000 x 4000 P at 1000 samples, 0 compression PNG format. ET til\u0027 it finishes 5 hours. Im going to leave it on over night. Hope you guys are ready because its coming.\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/YoEKivF.png\u0022 alt=\u0022YoEKivF.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lhathron the Elf","CreatedById":118706,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-18T00:41:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ghostbuzzer7\u0022 data-cite=\u0022ghostbuzzer7\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EIt is being made currently at 3000 x 4000 P at 1000 samples, 0 compression PNG format. ET til\u0027 it finishes 5 hours. Im going to leave it on over night. Hope you guys are ready because its coming.\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/YoEKivF.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://i.imgur.com/YoEKivF.png\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELooking forward to it!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ghostbuzzer7","CreatedById":138096,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-18T17:00:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHere it is the moment of precisely 5 hours 44 minutes of a render, 30 minutes of gimp I present to you \u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/sufTZC1.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022sufTZC1.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENow after twenty years of this poster being out to the public. It begins to so wear away.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/aNUiot4.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022aNUiot4.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EWhat it looked like before the rendering\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/rmo5IE4.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022rmo5IE4.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECant wait to see a everyone\u0027s poster\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fengist","CreatedById":78435,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-19T00:41:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWell, not exactly a recruiting poster but, it was me just goofin off after seeing this challenge. Not my greatest effort, but you get the um... picture.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis is for all of you who think Red Bull is the ultimate energy drink.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.datainterlock.com/Kerbal/Oxidizer.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022Oxidizer.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-19T03:55:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHere is my entry, kind of a futuristic poster:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/oNcrYBt.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022oNcrYBt.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGimp \u002B old mission to duna.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rolanvorxariat","CreatedById":117146,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-19T05:08:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAre we allowed to submit hand-drawn ones? Like, the ones on paper?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sidereus","CreatedById":135263,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-19T08:22:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMy (edited) entry:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/7U0Z4JO.png?1\u0022 alt=\u00227U0Z4JO.png?1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EETA: Added in some effects I was going to do yesterday but forgot.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-20T06:55:49Z\u0022 title=\u002204/20/2015 06:55  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 20, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Sidereus\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mystogon","CreatedById":141347,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-24T18:49:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENot the best but.. Some KSP Propaganda EDIT : down scaled the resolution because it took up too much space on the page\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/B8YtF0n.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022B8YtF0n.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-24T20:52:58Z\u0022 title=\u002204/24/2015 08:52  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 24, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Mystogon\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jean Deaux","CreatedById":59842,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-25T14:28:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i1365.photobucket.com/albums/r747/jdeaux44/KSP%20Recruitment_zpsck7djxsz.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP%20Recruitment_zpsck7djxsz.jpg\u0022\u003E\n"}]}